A further set of CsA analogues was developed, fine-tuned by derivatization at MeBmt residue 1 of CsA and a FK506 derivative with different properties regarding the inhibition of drug-Cyp/FKBP complexes, CaN phosphatase-, NFAT activities (Fig. 1
, Table 2
). Synthesis of drug derivatives compounds 1 and 2 were previously described (Prell et al., 2013). The CsA derivatives 3, 4, 5 were synthesized as recently published (Malesevic et al., 2013). The chemical synthesis of the non-immunosuppressive FK506 analogue 6 starting from the parent drug FK506 will be published elsewhere.
